    },
    "innerText": "(12) 2. Kesivaggo"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "1. Kesisuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "111"
      },
      ". Dutiyassa ",
      " paṭhame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "kesī"
      },
      "ti tassa nāmaṃ. Assadamme sāretīti ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "assadammasārathi. Saṇhenapi vinetī"
      },
      "tiādīsu tassa anucchavikaṃ sakkāraṃ katvā subhojanaṃ bhojetvā madhurapānaṃ pāyetvā muduvacanena samudācaritvā damento saṇhena dameti nāma, jāṇubandhanamukhabandhanādīhi ceva patodavijjhanakasābhighātapharusavacanehi ca damento pharusena dameti nāma, kālena kālaṃ tadubhayaṃ karonto saṇhapharusena dameti nāma."
    ],
    "innerText": "111. Dutiyassa paṭhame kesīti tassa nāmaṃ. Assadamme sāretīti assadammasārathi. Saṇhenapi vinetītiādīsu tassa anucchavikaṃ sakkāraṃ katvā subhojanaṃ bhojetvā madhurapānaṃ pāyetvā muduvacanena samudācaritvā damento saṇhena dameti nāma, jāṇubandhanamukhabandhanādīhi ceva patodavijjhanakasābhighātapharusavacanehi ca damento pharusena dameti nāma, kālena kālaṃ tadubhayaṃ karonto saṇhapharusena dameti nāma."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "2. Javasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "112"
      },
      ". Dutiye ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ajjavenā"
      },
      "ti ujukabhāvena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Javenā"
      },
      "ti padavegena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Khantiyā"
      },
      "ti adhivāsanakkhantiyā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Soraccenā"
      },
      "ti sucibhāvasīlena. Puggalaguṇaṅgesu ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "javenā"
      },
      "ti ñāṇajavena. Sesamettha uttānatthameva."
    ],
    "innerText": "112. Dutiye ajjavenāti ujukabhāvena. Javenāti padavegena. Khantiyāti adhivāsanakkhantiyā. Soraccenāti sucibhāvasīlena. Puggalaguṇaṅgesu javenāti ñāṇajavena. Sesamettha uttānatthameva."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "3. Patodasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "113"
      },
      ". Tatiye ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "patodacchāya"
      },
      "nti vijjhanatthaṃ ukkhittassa patodassa chāyaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṃvijjatī"
      },
      "ti ‘‘javo me gahetabbo’’ti sallakkhaṇavasena saṃvijjati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṃvegaṃ āpajjatī"
      },
      "ti saṃvegaṃ paṭipajjati ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "lomavedhaviddho"
      },
      "ti lomakūpe patodavedhena viddhamatto. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cammavedhaviddho"
      },
      "ti chavicammaṃ chindantena patodavedhena viddho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aṭṭhivedhaviddho"
      },
      "ti aṭṭhiṃ bhindantena vedhena viddho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kāyenā"
      },
      "ti nāmakāyena. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paramasacca"
      },
      "nti nibbānaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sacchikarotī"
      },
      "ti passati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paññāyā"
      },
      "ti sahavipassanāya maggapaññāya."
    ],
    "innerText": "113. Tatiye patodacchāyanti vijjhanatthaṃ ukkhittassa patodassa chāyaṃ. Saṃvijjatīti ‘‘javo me gahetabbo’’ti sallakkhaṇavasena saṃvijjati. Saṃvegaṃ āpajjatīti saṃvegaṃ paṭipajjati lomavedhaviddhoti lomakūpe patodavedhena viddhamatto. Cammavedhaviddhoti chavicammaṃ chindantena patodavedhena viddho. Aṭṭhivedhaviddhoti aṭṭhiṃ bhindantena vedhena viddho. Kāyenāti nāmakāyena. Paramasaccanti nibbānaṃ. Sacchikarotīti passati. Paññāyāti sahavipassanāya maggapaññāya."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "4. Nāgasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "114"
      },
      ". Catutthe ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "aṭṭhiṃ katvā"
      },
      "ti aṭṭhiko hutvā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tiṇavaninnādasaddāna"
      },
      "nti ettha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "tiṇavo"
      },
      "ti ḍiṇḍimo, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ninnādasaddo"
      },
      "ti sabbesampi ekatomissito mahāsaddo. Ḍaṃsādīsu ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ḍaṃsā"
      },
      "ti piṅgalamakkhikā, ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "makasā"
      },
      " makasāva. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Khippaññeva gantā hotī"
      },
      "ti sīlasamādhipaññāvimuttivimuttiñāṇadassanāni pūretvā sīghameva gantā hoti."
    ],
    "innerText": "114. Catutthe aṭṭhiṃ katvāti aṭṭhiko hutvā. Tiṇavaninnādasaddānanti ettha tiṇavoti ḍiṇḍimo, ninnādasaddoti sabbesampi ekatomissito mahāsaddo. Ḍaṃsādīsu ḍaṃsāti piṅgalamakkhikā, makasā makasāva. Khippaññeva gantā hotīti sīlasamādhipaññāvimuttivimuttiñāṇadassanāni pūretvā sīghameva gantā hoti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "5. Ṭhānasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "115"
      },
      ". Pañcame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "ṭhānānī"
      },
      "ti kāraṇāni. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Anatthāya saṃvattatī"
      },
      "ti ahitāya avaḍḍhiyā saṃvattati. Ettha ca paṭhamaṃ opātakkhaṇanamacchabandhanasandhicchedanādibhedaṃ sadukkhaṃ savighātaṃ pāpakammaṃ veditabbaṃ, dutiyaṃ samajīvikānaṃ gihīnaṃ pupphacchaḍḍakādikammaṃ sudhākoṭṭana-gehacchādanaasuciṭṭhānasammajjanādikammañca ",
      " veditabbaṃ, tatiyaṃ surāpānagandhavilepanamālāpiḷandhanādikammañceva assādavasena pavattaṃ pāṇātipātādikammañca veditabbaṃ, catutthaṃ dhammassavanatthāya gamanakāle suddhavatthacchādana-mālāgandhādīnaṃ ādāya gamanaṃ ",
      " cetiyavandanaṃ bodhivandanaṃ madhuradhammakathāsavanaṃ pañcasīlasamādānanti evamādīsu somanassasampayuttaṃ kusalakammaṃ veditabbaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Purisathāme"
      },
      "ti purisassa ñāṇathāmasmiṃ. Sesadvayepi eseva nayo."
    ],
    "innerText": "115. Pañcame ṭhānānīti kāraṇāni. Anatthāya saṃvattatīti ahitāya avaḍḍhiyā saṃvattati. Ettha ca paṭhamaṃ opātakkhaṇanamacchabandhanasandhicchedanādibhedaṃ sadukkhaṃ savighātaṃ pāpakammaṃ veditabbaṃ, dutiyaṃ samajīvikānaṃ gihīnaṃ pupphacchaḍḍakādikammaṃ sudhākoṭṭana-gehacchādanaasuciṭṭhānasammajjanādikammañca veditabbaṃ, tatiyaṃ surāpānagandhavilepanamālāpiḷandhanādikammañceva assādavasena pavattaṃ pāṇātipātādikammañca veditabbaṃ, catutthaṃ dhammassavanatthāya gamanakāle suddhavatthacchādana-mālāgandhādīnaṃ ādāya gamanaṃ cetiyavandanaṃ bodhivandanaṃ madhuradhammakathāsavanaṃ pañcasīlasamādānanti evamādīsu somanassasampayuttaṃ kusalakammaṃ veditabbaṃ. Purisathāmeti purisassa ñāṇathāmasmiṃ. Sesadvayepi eseva nayo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "6. Appamādasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "116"
      },
      ". Chaṭṭhe ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "yato kho"
      },
      "ti yadā kho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Samparāyikassā"
      },
      "ti desanāmattametaṃ, khīṇāsavo pana neva samparāyikassa, na diṭṭhadhammikassa maraṇassa bhāyati. Sova idha adhippeto. Keci pana ‘‘sammādiṭṭhi bhāvitāti vacanato sotāpannaṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbepi ariyā adhippetā’’ti vadanti."
    ],
    "innerText": "116. Chaṭṭhe yato khoti yadā kho. Samparāyikassāti desanāmattametaṃ, khīṇāsavo pana neva samparāyikassa, na diṭṭhadhammikassa maraṇassa bhāyati. Sova idha adhippeto. Keci pana ‘‘sammādiṭṭhi bhāvitāti vacanato sotāpannaṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbepi ariyā adhippetā’’ti vadanti."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "7. Ārakkhasuttavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "117"
      },
      ". Sattame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "attarūpenā"
      },
      "ti attano anurūpena anucchavikena, hitakāmenāti attho. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Rajanīyesū"
      },
      "ti ",
      " rāgassa paccayabhūtesu. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dhammesū"
      },
      "ti sabhāvesu, iṭṭhārammaṇesūti attho. Evaṃ sabbattha nayo veditabbo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na rajjatī"
      },
      "ti diṭṭhivasena na rajjati. Sesapadesupi eseva nayo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Na ca pana samaṇavacanahetupi gacchatī"
      },
      "ti samaṇānaṃ paravādīnaṃ vacanahetupi attano diṭṭhiṃ pahāya tesaṃ diṭṭhivasena na gacchatīti attho. Idhāpi khīṇāsavova adhippeto."
    ],
    "innerText": "117. Sattame attarūpenāti attano anurūpena anucchavikena, hitakāmenāti attho. Rajanīyesūti rāgassa paccayabhūtesu. Dhammesūti sabhāvesu, iṭṭhārammaṇesūti attho. Evaṃ sabbattha nayo veditabbo. Na rajjatīti diṭṭhivasena na rajjati. Sesapadesupi eseva nayo. Na ca pana samaṇavacanahetupi gacchatīti samaṇānaṃ paravādīnaṃ vacanahetupi attano diṭṭhiṃ pahāya tesaṃ diṭṭhivasena na gacchatīti attho. Idhāpi khīṇāsavova adhippeto."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "8-10. Saṃvejanīyādisuttattayavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "118-120"
      },
      ". Aṭṭhame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dassanīyānī"
      },
      "ti passitabbayuttakāni. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Saṃvejanīyānī"
      },
      "ti saṃvegajanakāni. Navame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "jātibhaya"
      },
      "nti jātiṃ ārabbha uppajjanakabhayaṃ. Sesapadesupi eseva nayo. Dasame ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "aggibhaya"
      },
      "nti aggiṃ paṭicca uppajjanakabhayaṃ. Sesapadesupi eseva nayo."
    ],
    "innerText": "118-120. Aṭṭhame dassanīyānīti passitabbayuttakāni. Saṃvejanīyānīti saṃvegajanakāni. Navame jātibhayanti jātiṃ ārabbha uppajjanakabhayaṃ. Sesapadesupi eseva nayo. Dasame aggibhayanti aggiṃ paṭicca uppajjanakabhayaṃ. Sesapadesupi eseva nayo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "centered"
    },
    "innerText": "Kesivaggo dutiyo."
  }
]